This is a list of characters from the Showtime TV series Dexter, its sequel miniseries Dexter: New Blood, and the Jeff Lindsay novels, including Darkly Dreaming Dexter (on which the show was based), Dearly Devoted Dexter, Dexter in the Dark, Dexter by Design, and Dexter Is Delicious.
